<H1>LaTeX Counters</H1>Everything LaTeX numbers for you has a counter =
associated=20
with it. The name of the counter is the same as the name of the =
environment or=20
command that produces the number, except with no \. Below is a list of =
the=20
counters used LaTeX's standard document styles to control numbering.=20
