  <TR>
    <TD>subsection=20
    <TD>equation=20
    <TD>mpfootnote=20
    <TD>enumiv=20
  <TR>
    <TD>subsubsection </TR></TBODY></TABLE>Here are the commands to be =
used with=20
counters:=20
